sequenceDiagram
    actor Participant
    participant RW as «view»<br>:RegisterWindow
    participant PW as «view»<br>:ParticipantProfileWindow
    participant RUC as «controller»<br>:RegisteredUserController
    participant PPC as «controller»<br>:ParticipantProfileController
    participant P as Participant

    note over Participant,P: USE CASE 1: REGISTER ACCOUNT
    Participant->>+RW: fill details & submit
    RW->>+RUC: store(request)
    RUC->>+P: create()
    P-->>-RUC: participant created
    RUC-->>-RW: return redirect
    RW-->>-Participant: show success message

    note over Participant,P: USE CASE 2: VIEW ACCOUNT
    Participant->>+PW: request profile page
    PW->>+PPC: index()
    PPC->>+P: get details
    P-->>-PPC: return data
    PPC-->>-PW: return view with data
    PW-->>-Participant: display profile

    note over Participant,P: USE CASE 3: EDIT ACCOUNT
    Participant->>+PW: submit updated details
    PW->>+PPC: update(request)
    PPC->>+P: save()
    P-->>-PPC: update confirmed
    PPC-->>-PW: return redirect
    PW-->>-Participant: show updated profile
